+~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
+The 'ZMQ_THREAD_NAME_PREFIX' argument gets the numeric prefix of each thread
+created for the internal context's thread pool.
